overview:
DuckHook Media is a media firm solely dedicated to the golfing industry. With industry leading technology, DuckHook Media provides golf courses, clubs and resorts, teaching professionals, golf retail stores and driving ranges with online media products. DuckHook Media’s portfolio of products consists of mobile optimized websites, e-commerce websites, mobile apps with m-commerce capabilities, custom video projects and search engine marketing and optimization. To find out more about DuckHook Media you can visit our website at www.DuckHookMedia.com.

DuckHook Media also owns and operates DuckHooked.com™- a complete golfers website. With an engaging and interactive social networking site for golfers of all ages and skill levels, DuckHooked.com also features a robust directory for golf courses, golf driving ranges and golf retail stores. In addition, DuckHooked.com™ includes online tee times; golf handicap tracker & scoring analysis; news & weather; golf articles and videos with tips; golf course and golf equipment reviews; groups to network with other golfers; classified ads for golf equipment; forums and more – DuckHooked.com™ is jam-packed with features!
